
Video
=====

- introduce "videos" to specify once the video field. The key is used as an alias (if string, try to lookup, otherwise use the string as an url)
- Check video works everywhere
  - Mac Chrome
  - Mac Firefox
  - Mac Safari
  - Windows Chrome
  - Windows IE
  - Linux Firefox
  - Linux Chromium
  - Android Firefox
  - Android Chrome
  - iOS Safari
- run the tests

